        advanced: 'Create complete cookie consent system. Banner position: bottom bar (default), bottom corner popup, or center modal. Initial state: show on first visit, respect Do Not Track if enabled. Content: clear explanation of cookie usage, link to full privacy policy. Cookie categories: essential (always on), analytics, marketing, preferences - each with toggle and description. Quick actions: "Accept All", "Reject All", "Customize" buttons. Customization modal: detailed category explanations, individual toggles, Save Preferences button. Essential cookies: cannot be disabled, explain why. Cookie list: expandable list of actual cookies per category with purpose and duration. Remember choice: store preference in cookie/localStorage, expiry after 1 year. Re-consent: trigger on policy change, show "Updated" badge. Minimize: after choice, show small button to reopen preferences. Legal compliance: GDPR (EU), CCPA (California) option switches, appropriate language. A/B variants: different copy and layouts for testing. No banner if consented: only show settings link in footer. Integration: fire consent events for analytics tools to respect. Accessibility: focus trap in modal, keyboard operable, screen reader announcements.'
